body_html:
The code runs fine, but it is hard to tell if there is difference in speed, compared to TF 1.3.

I know that the warning has been there for a long time, but could it be that the implementation of some of the operators that I use changed between the two versions and causes the implicit conversion and hence the warning? In any case, it is very strange that I was not getting the warning in 1.3 if nothing changed.
